        <abstract> 
<p>Sale of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> requires new edition [3d (Apr 1861)].</p> 
            <p>Further discussion of geological elevation and subsidence in Europe. Compares evidence to that of South America. His theory that semi-fluid matter underlies earth’s crust.</p>
            <p>Mentions David Forbes’s explanation of South American nitrate deposits.</p>
            <p>Has followed CL’s advice not to reply directly to reviewers.</p>
        </abstract>
